[{'recipients': ['FRA'], 'body': "France, confirmed - I'm moving F HOL to KIE this spring and F NTH to DEN to complete the German collapse. With your A BER pressing toward KIE and A BUR taking MUN, Germany has nowhere to run. KIE and DEN go to England, MUN and BER stay French - that's the clean division. Execute your moves and I'll execute mine. Germany ends this season."}, {'recipients': ['GER'], 'body': "Germany, I've heard your proposal and I'm genuinely weighing it - France at 6 centers is dangerous. However, I need something concrete: if you can demonstrate you're moving A MUN to BUR and A KIE to BER as you say, I will hold F HOL defensively and not press KIE. But I need your commitment that DEN transfers to England peacefully as compensation for my restraint. Without that concession, I have no reason to hold back."}, {'recipients': ['RUS'], 'body': "Russia, France is now the dominant power with 6 centers and growing - they hold BER and threaten to sweep Germany entirely. I'm taking steps to limit French expansion in the north. I propose we maintain our current positions in NWY and SWE without conflict, and both focus pressure on the real threats. A stable north benefits us both while the continental powers exhaust themselves."}]
